Type: Package
Package: misskappa
Title: Inference for agreement coefficients with incomplete data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonas", "Moss", , "jonas.moss.statistics@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6876-6964"))
Description: Provides consistent and efficient estimation and inference for weighted kappa coefficients 
    (Fleiss, Conger, and Brennan–Prediger) under missing data. The methods apply to both 
    rating-level data and count-level data, and support various weighting schemes. Estimation 
    is based on maximum likelihood and the delta method.
